<div class="about">
    <div class="about-title">
        <h1>Welcome to Pender Mifflin</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="outer-about-box">
        <div class="about-box">
            <div class="about-content">
                <p>
                    Pender Mifflin Inc. (stock symbol PMI) is a micro-cap regional pen supply distributor with an emphasis on servicing small-business clients. With a corporate office in New York City, Pender Mifflin
                    has branches in Buffalo, Albany, Utica, Scranton, Akron, Camden, Nashua and Yonkers.
                    Pender Mifflin Inc. provides its customers quality pens and pen products, pen values and the expertise required for making informed buying choices. We provide our products and services with a
                    dedication to the highest degree of integrity and quality of customer satisfaction, developing long-term professional relationships with employees that develop pride, creating a stable working
                    environment and company spirit.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


